column5: I just got back from the B1 Anglers meeting, anybody who's anybody in the bass fishing scene is there. Bob Izumi and Wayne, the Fishin' Canada guys(all four  of them) ,Charles Sim, Mike Desforge, Rob Laframboise(all the way from Sault St. Marie. Mark Weare from Nova Scotia and many more. Man what did I get myself into  :worthy: ...   Anyways I've got to get some sleep(I hope)up at 2:30AM.
